OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud around the
OL,6,Fcoast and hills but mostly fine and
OL,7,Fdry to start. Cloud breaks rapidly
OL,8,Faway from coastal areas to a sunny and
OL,9,Fdry day. Light northerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening for
OL,12,Fmuch of the region. Patchy cloud
OL,13,Fbecomes widespread from the east
OL,14,Fovernight but expected to remain dry.
OL,15,FLight northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
