OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy day across the
OL,6,Fregion with patchy drizzle possible.
OL,7,FGreater potential for sunny spells in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon and evening. Light,
OL,9,Flocally stronger along coasts,
OL,10,Fnortherly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,13,Fand dry day on Sunday with fresh
OL,14,Fnortherly winds. Cloudier through
OL,15,FMonday and Tuesday with potential for
OL,16,Fpatchy rain at times and light
OL,17,Fnortherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
